                  - Warehouses that have been requested registration is displayed yellow in the 'warehouse registration
                  list'.<br>
                  - Warehouses that have been rejected are displayed red in the 'Warehouse Registration List'. After
                  checking the reason for rejection through the "View" button, click "Delete" to remove it from the
