                  - Select the "INFO" button in the warehouse "My Warehouse" you want to edit.<br>
                  - Select the "edit" button on the right of "Warehouse Info".<br>
                  - Edit the warehouse information and select the "apply" button.<br>
                  - Warehouse name and address cannot be changed.<br>
                </p>
              </div>
            </li>
