                <p>
                  - You can check the current warehouse usage status by clicking the "info" button in "My
                  Warehouse".<br>
                  - In "Warehouse Usage", the warehouse that are currently being used by buyer are in green, and the
                  ones waiting to be used are in yellow.<br>
                  - Previous warehouse usage history can be checked in "Previous Warehouse Usage".<br>
                  - You can check user information by using the "info" button in all usage history.<br>
                </p>
